                        "name": "Brutal Blow",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "The spinesnapper makes a claw or weapon Strike. If it hits, in addition to dealing damage, the creature must attempt a DC 22 Fortitude saving throw, with the following effects. <br/><b>Critical Success</b> The creature is unaffected and the spinesnapper is flat-footed until the start of its next turn.<br/><b>Success</b> The creature is unaffected.<br/><b>Failure</b> The creature is pushed 10 feet.<br/><b>Critical Failure</b> The target is pushed 10 feet and knocked prone.",
